                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noreferrer"
                            style="text-decoration: none; color: black;"
                    >
                        AMCM Extends Exchange Period for Zodiacal and Olympic Winter Games Notes; Online Subscribers
                        Urged to Utilize Added Days
                    </a>
                </mj-text>

                <mj-text mj-class="location">
                    Asia - Macao
                </mj-text>

                <mj-text mj-class="location">
                    Monetary Authority of Macao
                </mj-text>

                <mj-text mj-class="date">
                    Wednesday, August 09, 2023
                </mj-text>

                <mj-text mj-class="body-text">
                    The deadline for exchanging the zodiacal notes of the Years of the Tiger and the Rabbit, as well as
                    the notes for celebrating the 24th Edition of the Olympic Winter Games, had been set as August 11,
                    2023. However, to accommodate residents, the AMCM has authorized an additional exchange period
                    running from August 14 to 18, 2023. Subscribers who registered online and are yet to exchange their
                    notes are advised to do so within the extra period at the earlier chosen location. For any further
                    information or clarification, the AMCM can be contacted through the hotline telephone numbers
                    28565071/28565072, or their website during office hours.
                </mj-text>

